   <identificationInfo>
      <resourceName>MINELex</resourceName>
      <description>MINELex (Multilingual, Interoperable Named Entity Lexicon) contains Named Entities (NEs) for English (974,567), Italian (125,806) and Spanish (137,583) connected to general domain lexicons (English WordNet, WordNet and the Italian SIMPLE-CLIPS) and two ontologies (SUMO and SIMPLE), in a format compliant with the ISO Lexical Markup Framework (LMF). Automatically built, it has been applied to validate questions regarding NEs in a state-of-the-art Question Answering system providing a 28% increment in accuracy.</description>
